{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_04_03",
  "title": "白石千紗 3話 二人で描いた夢",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お待たせしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry to keep you waiting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.2675324559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "デザイナーさんから話を聞いてきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just had a talk with the designer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1613175474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それで、デザインが違うってどういうことなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what do you mean by the design being different?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4008657892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.0675324559
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "それが、行き違いがあったらしくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems there was a misunderstanding…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.0675324559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "打ち合わせでデザインの修正をお願いしたところが\n私のイメージと違う仕上がりになっていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The modifications we discussed during the meeting\nresulted in a design different from my original vision.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.7699087709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.3341991226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "最近忙しかったので、メールと電話だけでやり取りして\nデザイナーさんに手直しをお任せしたんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I've been busy lately‚ we communicated through emails and phone calls‚\nand I entrusted the revisions to the designer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.2740909576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "メールだと希望がうまく伝わらなかったみたいで……\nごめんなさい、ちゃんと確認しなかった私のミスです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it seems my preferences didn't come across well via email…\nI'm sorry‚ it's my bad for not confirming properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.1250280738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.7008657892
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "だから千紗のイメージとずれたデザインになったのか\n今から修正は出来ないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ the design turned out different because of this misunderstanding.\nCan't it be corrected now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3672014364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.8675324559
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "細かい修正が重なって、今とはほぼ別の形になります\nつまり……一から作り直しです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With multiple adjustments‚ it'd end up being completely different from now.\nIn other words‚ we would have to start over….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7673501133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.5008657892
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "もう時間がありません。私のイメージとは\n違いますけど、今回はこのままでいくしか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no more time. Even though it's different from\nmy vision‚ we have no choice but to go with this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0174190327,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.6008657892
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗はそれでいいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that really okay with you‚ Chisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.6008657892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "いいも何も、そうするしか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not about whether it's okay or not…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9398316502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.3731649835
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "でも納得してないんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you're not satisfied with it‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3731649835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.9731649835
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "私のわがままでみなさんに迷惑をかけられません\n私が我慢して丸く収まるなら、それで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't inconvenience everyone with my selfishness.\nIf I can make it work by suppressing my own feelings‚ then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.088600607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "周りがどう思うかは関係ない。千紗はどうしたいんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It doesn't matter what others think. What do you want‚ Chisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4398316502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.6160279393
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "それは……出来ることなら直したいです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… If possible‚ I want to fix it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6160279393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.282694606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "本当は……\nお姉ちゃんと着るこの衣装だけは妥協したくありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The truth is‚ for this outfit that I'll wear with my sister‚\nI don't want to compromise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5476554513,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.8897861475
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "中途半端は嫌です\n私は最高の衣装でお姉ちゃんとライブがしたいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want something halfway.\nI want to perform with my sister in the best outfit possible!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8897861475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "これは私が思う最高の衣装じゃありません！\nお願いします、やり直させて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I want or don't want doesn't matter.\nI mustn't inconvenience everyone by indulging myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。予算とスケジュールは俺がなんとかする\nだから千紗は納得のいく衣装を作ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ I'll handle the budget and schedule somehow.\nSo‚ Chisa‚ make a outfit that satisfies you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それだと{user}さんの負担が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ that will be a burden on you‚ {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルが力を発揮出来るようにするのも仕事だ\n千紗は遠慮しないで、もっと俺を頼ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Making sure idols can shine is also part of my job.\nChisa‚ don't hesitate to count on me more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます……\n必ず最高の衣装を作ってみせます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much…\nI will definitely create the best outfit!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5833.333333300005,
          "startTime": 141.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（衣装優先でスケジュールを組み直して……）\n（それでもユニットバトルに間に合うかどうか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Rescheduling for the outfit‚ but…）\n（Will we make it in time for the unit battle with this change…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（千紗も練習で沙季とぎくしゃくしているようだし）\n（問題は山積みだな。これから忙しくなりそうだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Chisa seems to be having some difficulties with her practice too…）\n（We have a lot of problems on our plate. It's going to get busy.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
