    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ここまでよく頑張ったな。千紗と沙季が決勝まで\n勝ち上がってくれたから新しい衣装が間に合ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've both worked really hard. Thanks to Chisa and Saki advancing\nto the finals‚ we were able to finish the new outfits in time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "はい、決勝に衣装が間に合って良かったです\nお姉ちゃんも新しい衣装を見て凄く喜んでました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'm glad we made it in time for the finals.\nMy sister was really happy to see the new outfit too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "衣装合わせの時から\nお姉ちゃんはこの衣装を気に入ってくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From the outfit fitting‚ my sister liked this one a lot…\nShe said‚ \"This outfit is perfect for us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "「この衣装、私達にぴったり……。子供の頃に二人で\n描いた夢が叶ったみたいだわ」って言ってくれたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's like a dream we both drew when we were kids\nhas come true.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんがこの衣装を素敵に着こなすのを見て\n私……感動して泣きそうになっちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Watching my sister fabulously wear this outfit‚\nI… felt so moved that I almost cried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs021.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんが言ってました\nアイドルとしていろんな衣装を着てきたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My sister said‚\nI've worn many outfits as an idol‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs022.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに幸せな気持ちにしてくれた衣装はないって……\nこの衣装は、お姉ちゃんのお気に入りだって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but… this one has made me the happiest.\nShe considers this outfit her favorite…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "満足するのはまだ早いぞ\n決勝ではこの衣装に見合うパフォーマンスをしないとな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's too early to be satisfied. In the finals‚\nyou need to deliver a performance that matches this outfit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　お姉ちゃんと約束したんです。この衣装で……\n二人で最高の姉妹ユニットになろうって……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! We promised each other‚ with this outfit…\nto become the best sister unit!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "だから、行ってきます！\nお姉ちゃんと一緒に歌ってきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ here I go!\nI'll sing with my sister!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 243.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 244.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（そうして千紗と沙季は、決勝のステージで）\n（素晴らしいパフォーマンスを披露した）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And so‚ Chisa and Saki delivered an amazing performance）\n（on the finals stage.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（新しい衣装で沙季と一緒に歌う千紗は）\n（宣言していた通りに輝いて見えた……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And as promised‚\nChisa shone brightly as she sang with Saki）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 259.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "昨日はお疲れ様\nそれと、改めて……ユニットバトル優勝おめでとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job yesterday.\nAlso‚ once again… congratulations on winning the unit battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs025.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "決勝のパフォーマンスも衣装も大好評だそうだ\n頑張った甲斐があったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard that both your performance in the finals\nand the outfit were highly praised. Your hard work paid off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs026.m4a",
      "text": "あの衣装を作れたのは、{user}さんが\n背中を押してくれたおかげです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was able to create that outfit\nbecause you supported me‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs027.m4a",
      "text": "私のわがままで迷惑をかけてしまって\nすみませんでした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for causing trouble\nwith my stubbornness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は普段が遠慮し過ぎだから\nたまにわがままを言うくらいがちょうどいいさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ you're usually too modest‚\nso it's just right to be a little selfish sometimes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 289.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "あの衣装が話題になれば\n今後はファッション関係の仕事が増えるかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that outfit make a wave‚\nyou might get more fashion-related work in the future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 294.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs028.m4a",
      "text": "ファッション関係……\nお姉ちゃんはあまりやらないお仕事ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fashion-related work…\nMy sister doesn't do much of that kind of job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs029.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんと一緒に歌ってみて思ったんです\nお姉ちゃんに憧れてずっと後を追いかけてきたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After singing with my sister‚ I realized\nthat I've been following her footsteps because I admired her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs030.m4a",
      "text": "もしかしたら、お姉ちゃんみたいに\nならなくてもいいのかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But maybe‚\nI don't have to become like my sister…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 315.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs031.m4a",
      "text": "私は私らしいアイドルになればいいのかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Perhaps‚ I can be an idol just the way I am",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 318.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-chs032.m4a",
      "text": "私、これからもお姉ちゃんと一緒に……\nお姉ちゃんに負けないように、頑張ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From now on‚ I'll keep doing my best\nnot to lose to my sister!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 328.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_04_03-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "（姉妹ユニットが姉離れのきっかけに、か……）\n（独り立ちし始めた千紗のこれからが楽しみだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The sister unit could be Chisa's starting point for becoming）\n（more independent… I'm looking forward to Chisa's future.）",
        "id": ""
      },
